      right: ["Severe cyanosis with oxygen saturation <70%","Hypercyanotic spell with profound desaturation and altered consciousness","Metabolic acidosis indicating inadequate tissue oxygenation","Signs of heart failure: tachycardia, hepatomegaly, edema, poor perfusion","Ductal closure in a PDA-dependent neonate: sudden worsening cyanosis and cardiovascular collapse","Post-Fontan complications: protein-losing enteropathy, effusions, arrhythmias"]
