      right: ["QRS >160 ms with ventricular arrhythmias","Seizures (generalized tonic-clonic)","Cardiovascular collapse with refractory hypotension","PEA arrest or ventricular fibrillation","Coma with loss of airway protective reflexes","Metabolic acidosis with pH <7.1 (worsens free TCA levels and cardiotoxicity)"]
